product.name: "It Had To Be Yule" CD
product.description:
Lost Moon Radio, LA’s underground comedy darling, presents the group’s first full-length studio album.  From the glam-rock hit “Personal Menorah”, to the choral masterpiece “Uncle Mort Is Coming”, It Had to be Yule captures the spirit of all the holidays in dry comedy and wet rock ‘n roll. 
1.	Lost Moon Radio Theme
2.	Holiday Greetings
3.	Christ, His Head is Crowning
4.	It's December 24th
5.	Christmas Memories
6.	Donna the Christmas Girl
7.	That Lonely Road
8.	Down with an Elf
9.	Dear Diary
10.	I'd Have You In A Manager
11.	Patrick Stewart's A Christmas Story
12.	Personal Menorah
13.	Uncle Mort Is Coming
14.	My Beloved Sarah
15.	Next Year
16.	Final Reflections
17.	Jupiter Jack Theme
